Heartseeker {{champion:22}} 

Nightraven {{champion:114}} 

Bilgewater {{champion:55}} 

Frostblade {{champion:39}} 

Having long loading times when ^these skins are in the game gets you distracted to the point where you want to go do something _else_.

Want to counter Riven hard? Play {{champion:86}} or {{champion:106}} 

I never lose to her laning phase, her late game snowballing is bullshit, especially with how easy it is for her to KS a couple kills and undo any damage I did during the laning phase.

But even if she is fed, and you are somewhat well farmed those two fuck her up real well.
